than a simple change there.

00:43:18.104 --> 00:43:20.520
In other words, although they
are identical before they're

00:43:20.520 --> 00:43:22.920
changed, there are
certain ways of changing

00:43:22.920 --> 00:43:25.260
one which look natural,
which don't look natural

00:43:25.260 --> 00:43:25.886
in the other.

00:43:25.886 --> 00:43:27.510
