theoretical representations

00:43:34.800 --> 00:43:36.670
for exactly the same physics.

00:43:36.670 --> 00:43:40.327
And knows that
they're all equivalent

00:43:40.327 --> 00:43:42.660
and that nobody is ever going
to be able to decide which

00:43:42.660 --> 00:43:43.904
