hoping that they'll give him

00:43:46.320 --> 00:43:49.260
different ideas for guessing.

00:43:49.260 --> 00:43:51.480
Incidentally, that reminds
me of another thing

00:43:51.480 --> 00:43:54.610
and that is that the
philosophy or the ideas

00:43:54.610 --> 00:43:56.324
around the theory--

00:43:56.324 --> 00:43:57.900
there are a lot of ideas.

00:43:57.900 --> 00:44:01.860
You say, I believe there is
a space-time or something

00:44:01.860 --> 00:44:04.730
like that in order to
discuss your analyses.

00:44:04.730 --> 00:44:07.710
That these ideas
change enormously

00:44:07.710 --> 00:44:10.060
