changes in the theory.

00:44:10.060 --> 00:44:12.210
In other words, for
instance, Newton's ideas

00:44:12.210 --> 00:44:16.170
about space and time agree
with experiment very well.

00:44:16.170 --> 00:44:20.220
But in order to get the correct
motion of the orbit of Mercury,

00:44:20.220 --> 00:44:22.530
which was a tiny,
tiny difference,

00:44:22.530 --> 00:44:25.170
the difference in the character
of the theory with which you

00:44:25.170 --> 00:44:26.370
started was enormous.

00:44:26.370 --> 00:44:29.480
Reason is these are so
simple and so perfect.

00:44:29.480 --> 00:44:30.870
They produce definite results.

00:44:30.870 --> 00:44:32.080
In order to get
something that produces

00:44:32.080 --> 00:44:34.580
