00:44:52.920 --> 00:44:55.800
A philosophy, which is sometimes
called an understanding

00:44:55.800 --> 00:44:58.230
of the law, is simply a
way that a person holds

00:44:58.230 --> 00:45:02.670
the laws in his mind so as to
guess quickly at consequence.

00:45:02.670 --> 00:45:04.271
Some people have
said, and it's true

00:45:04.271 --> 00:45:06.270
for instance, in the case
of Maxwell's equations

00:45:06.270 --> 00:45:08.850
