to compute the answers

00:45:14.370 --> 00:45:16.680
so they agree with
experiment and is not

00:45:16.680 --> 00:45:20.970
necessarily to have a philosophy
or words about the equation.

00:45:20.970 --> 00:45:23.190
That's true in a sense.

00:45:23.190 --> 00:45:24.450
Yes and no.

00:45:24.450 --> 00:45:26.640
