you may be if you only

00:45:26.640 --> 00:45:28.890
guess the equation, you're
not prejudiced in yourself,

00:45:28.890 --> 00:45:29.980
and you'll guess better.

00:45:29.980 --> 00:45:32.480
On the other hand, maybe the
philosophy helped you to guess.

00:45:32.480 --> 00:45:34.590
It's very hard to say.

