half moon, and so on.

00:46:14.790 --> 00:46:16.610
Just calculate it only.

00:46:16.610 --> 00:46:20.400
Suppose that a young man went
to the astronomer and said,

00:46:20.400 --> 00:46:21.630
I have an idea.

00:46:21.630 --> 00:46:23.510
Maybe those things
